  "title": "PUMP ATTENDANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚨 URGENT HIRING - PETROL STATION 🚨</strong></p><p><strong>Position:  Pump Attendant 加油员</strong></p><p><strong>SalaryRange: $1600 - $2000</strong></p><p><u><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>●       Provide pleasant service by assisting customers in refueling vehicles 专业礼貌地为客户车辆添油</p><p>●       Assist in traffic control at the forecourt 协助站内的交通管理</p><p>●       General housekeeping and cleaning at station 油站的基本清理</p><p>●       Ad hoc tasks assigned by the immediate supervisor 其他直属主管分配的工作</p><p><strong>***Job Requirements***:</strong></p><p>●       Full Time & Part Time Position!!!! 全职和兼职！！！</p><p>●       Physical fit 身体状况良好</p><p>●       Able to start work immediately 能够立即开工</p><p>●       Able to perform shift work, and work on weekends or public holidays 需轮班，并可在周末或公共假期配合排班</p><p>●       Welcome residents to apply  欢迎本地居民</p><p>●       Location 工作地点：Multiple Location (多个地点)</p><p><em><strong>Benefits福利:</strong></em></p><p>Medical Coverage 医疗保险</p><p>Teamwork allowance 团队津贴</p><p>Festive allowance 节日津贴</p><p>Other attractive incentives 其他奖励</p><p>Uniform provided 提供工作制服</p><p>*** If you are interested, please call <em><strong>Mr. Shariff (91871435)， Ms. Mala (87113400), Mr. Hamley (85757832)</strong></em> </p><p>***有意者请联系 <em><strong>Mr.Shariff (91871435)， Ms. Mala (87113400), Mr. Hamley (85757832)</strong></em> </p>",
