    "description": "<p>Sinopec Hong Kong (Singapore) Pte Ltd is headquartered in Hong Kong that is wholly owned by China Petroleum &amp; Chemical Corporation. Our core business includes trading of gasoline, diesel, aviation fuel, fuel oil focusing in Asia Pacific Region. Meanwhile, we are also operating oil retailing business in Singapore. We are expanding our footprint in Singapore and Southeast Asia as well.&nbsp;We strive to create a good working environment. We offer a competitive remuneration package and excellent career development opportunities. We respect our staff's opinions and encourage them to unleash their full potential. Do join our awesome team and build up your career with us!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
